Poppy.move01.text: "What do you mean my hammer's too big?"

Poppy.move02.text: "If you're waiting for me to give up, you might be here a while."

Poppy.move04.text: "I sure do a lot of walking."

Poppy.move05.text: "Yep, it's even heavier than it looks."

Poppy.taunt02.text: "This hammer has two sides. Did you want to feel the other one too?"

Poppy.taunt03.text: "Fool me once, shame on you. Fool me twice, uh... hammer!"

Poppy.taunt04.text: "Could you maybe get out of the way? Y'know, so I don't have to flatten you."

Poppy.tauntGalio01.text: "You know, gargoyles and Yordles have a lot in common."

Poppy.tauntGaren01.text: "Oh, wow, Garen, do you think you could sign my shield?"

Poppy.tauntGaren02.text: "Garen, I think you might be the one!"

Poppy.tauntJarvan01.text: "A pleasure to fight for you, your majesty."

Poppy.tauntJayce01.text: "That's not a hammer! This is a hammer."

Poppy.tauntTaric01.text: "I'm about to hammer you in the jewels."

Poppy.joke02.text:
"A Demacian, a Noxian and a Freljordian walk into a tavern."
   "The barkeep asks, 'What'll it be?'"
   "The Demacian says, 'Uh, I'll have a wine.' No, wait, an ale! Yeah..."
   "Then the Noxian says, 'I'll have a... a wine.' Yeah, he wants a wine."
   "And the Freljordian says, 'I'll drink anything, so long as-' Wait, hold on, let me start over."

Poppy.joke07.text:
"A Noxian, a Targonian and a Piltie are robbing a bank."
   "The bank guy says, 'I'll give you whatever you want.'"
   "The Noxian says, 'I'll take whatever gold you got back there.'"
   "The Targonian says, 'Gimme' all your gemstones!'"
   "And the Piltie says, 'Can I own this ba- uh, I own this bank, so...' He doesn't want anything because he owns the bank..."

AurelionSol.start01.text: "They call me a comet. They call me a dragon. They have no words for my true form."

AurelionSol.start02.text: "Cower, worship, beg, they're all valid reactions."

AurelionSol.start03.text: "In a constantly shifting cosmos, a world this static is... refreshing."

AurelionSol.start04.text: "There simply are no other dragons like me."

AurelionSol.start06.text: "Hope. Wonder. Insignificance. Imagine what they'll feel when I complete the stars."

AurelionSol.attack03.text: "Let's end this on a high note!"

AurelionSol.attack05.text: "Never stand in the path of a star."

AurelionSol.attack07.text: "It's beyond too late to seek cover."

AurelionSol.attack11.text: "Lighten up, destruction needn't be a maudlin affair."

AurelionSol.attack12.text: "Suns never burn for the benefit of dust."

AurelionSol.attack19.text: "I'm going to throw a star at you now. Good luck."

AurelionSol.attack23.text: "Nothing a little star fire cannot fix."

AurelionSol.attackDragon01.text: "Terrestrial dragons - a study of flawed constitutions."

AurelionSol.attackDragon03.text: "You call yourself a dragon? You're low-flame at best."

AurelionSol.attackDragon04.text: "A dragon that still needs wings to fly? Keep trying, you'll get there."

AurelionSol.attackDragon05.text: "I did mean to call you back, but stars needed forging."

AurelionSol.move01.text: "This world holds the key to Targon's undoing."

AurelionSol.move02.text: "Targon has used me as its weapon for far too long."

AurelionSol.move04.text: "I would burn the cosmos to catch Targon in the flames."

AurelionSol.move05.text: "The depths of space crawl with terrible entities. Pray they ignore this world."

AurelionSol.move06.text: "There are countless colors, but I suppose a single rainbow was a good start."

AurelionSol.move07.text: "This sun is off its axis - it's been driving me crazy for eons now."

AurelionSol.move08.text: "Planetary life... the insufferable byproduct of dim stars."

AurelionSol.move10.text: "Nothing kindles wonder like the beauty of stars."

AurelionSol.move11.text: "Celestial dragons live and die by our own beautiful rules."

AurelionSol.move12.text: "Love is as real a force as gravity. Try it once in a while."

AurelionSol.move13.text: "Stars are not born, they are made... by me."

AurelionSol.move14.text: "A star's birth is as violent as it is breathtaking."

AurelionSol.move15.text: "I've waited millennia to watch Targon fall."

AurelionSol.move16.text: "All beings are made of the same stardust."

AurelionSol.move17.text: "With a few more basic elements I could really make this place shimmer."

AurelionSol.move18.text: "The stars are not to thank for any good luck one may experience."

AurelionSol.move19.text: "This sun could do with a new core."

AurelionSol.move20.text: "Any relevant species has been knocked back into the Stone Age once or twice."

AurelionSol.move21.text: "I wouldn't navigate by the stars. They are a work in progress."

AurelionSol.move22.text: "Each star is one of my hearts."

AurelionSol.move23.text: "My works are revered by worlds I have never even visited."

AurelionSol.move24.text: "Wherever I am is the fashionable part of the universe. Even here."

AurelionSol.move27.text: "A star is so much more than a luminous sphere of wonder."

AurelionSol.move28.text: "If you ask me, we have set the bar too low for sentience."

AurelionSol.move29.text: "My home is in the cosmos, amongst my stars."

AurelionSol.move30.text: "The stories they tell about me? They're probably true."

AurelionSol.move31.text: "All terrestrial dragons are but pale imitations of my kind."

AurelionSol.move32.text: "Perhaps there is more to this world than I thought - not much, but enough."

AurelionSol.move34.text: "Why does anyone wish upon a star?"

AurelionSol.move35.text: "Stars never align for anyone - except me, of course."

AurelionSol.move38.text: "Only when darkness overwhelms the heavens will Targon realise its folly."

AurelionSol.move40.text: "Targon will be the pyre from which I forge a new heaven."

AurelionSol.move41.text: "I see a universe drained of light and heat, where not even a story will survive."

AurelionSol.move42.text: "I grieve for every star never born."

AurelionSol.move44.text: "Whenever I think my work is complete, I end up back here, under this sun."

AurelionSol.moveEnemyBase01.text: "May I enter? Just joking - star dragons don't need permission."

AurelionSol.taunt01.text: "Your demise will be sung about for ages to come - only thanks to its proximity to me, of course."

AurelionSol.taunt02.text: "Your survival is not impossible, only very... very... very unlikely."

AurelionSol.taunt03.text: "I shall be the last thing you see. Lucky you."

AurelionSol.taunt04.text: "Make a wish. See if the stars answer. I'll wait."

AurelionSol.taunt05.text: "What is the definition of underwhelming? Oh, right! You."

AurelionSol.taunt06.text: "I used to wander the stars. Now I'm stuck down here, with you."

AurelionSol.taunt07.text: "On other worlds, there is emerging life more complex than you."

AurelionSol.tauntAhri01.text: "You aspire to be human? Oh, darling, there are so many other variants on mediocrity!"

AurelionSol.tauntAmumu01.text: "I am... overwhelmed by an emotion when you are not around. It is called... happiness."

AurelionSol.tauntAnnie01.text: "Mages are infants grasping at the machinery behind reality. At least you have a plausible excuse."

AurelionSol.tauntAzir01.text: "You Ascended certainly know how to pick an animal totem."

AurelionSol.tauntAzir02.text: "Your immortality is but a grain of sand in time's vast desert."

AurelionSol.tauntBard01.text: "Pick a dimension, Bard, you're confusing them!"

AurelionSol.tauntBard02.text: "Were you born this flat, or did you work at it?"

AurelionSol.tauntCaitlyn01.text: "The funnier the hat, the greater the prestige, right?"

AurelionSol.tauntCelestial01.trigger: Taunting an enemy with a Celestial skin

AurelionSol.tauntDiana01.text: "You and Leona embody the same light. Typical Targon redundancy."

AurelionSol.tauntDiana02.text: "It is always a moon's role to envy the stars."

AurelionSol.tauntDragonSlayer01.trigger: Taunting an enemy with a Dragon Slayer skin

AurelionSol.tauntDragonTrainerTristana01.text: "Oh, come on, have a little self-respect!"
AurelionSol.tauntDragonTrainerTristana01.trigger: Taunting an enemy Dragon Trainer Tristana

AurelionSol.tauntDunkmasterDarius01.text: "If dunking is the apex of this primitive sport, then I am the queen of space."

AurelionSol.tauntEkko01.text: "Made a mistake? Better rewind and repeat until you achieve mediocrity."

AurelionSol.tauntHuman01.text: "Ah, mankind. Ever fumbling from one brink of cataclysm to the next."

AurelionSol.tauntHuman02.text: "Humanity, surprisingly adept in the art of wrestling survival from the clutches of extinction."

AurelionSol.tauntHuman03.text: "As far as fauna goes, humans strike a firm... middle."

AurelionSol.tauntIllaoi02.text: "I've seen the main act. You're only a third-rate cover band."

AurelionSol.tauntIllaoi01.text: "You do not understand your god, Illaoi."

AurelionSol.tauntJhin.text: "Imagine what you could do with a larger canvas."

AurelionSol.tauntJinx01.text: "Life is short, go crazy once in a while, I get it."

AurelionSol.tauntLeona02.text: "You and Diana embody the same light. Typical Targon redundancy."

AurelionSol.tauntMalphite01.text: "There is a saying on this planet - "Dumb as a rock". It's not a compliment."

AurelionSol.tauntMissFortune01.text: "You are going to kill me? Dressed like that?"

AurelionSol.tauntNasus01.text: "Bravo, Nasus, you've ascended yourself into a dog! Now fetch me something more interesting."

AurelionSol.tauntNasus02.text: "I could teach an old dog millions of new tricks, but I simply don't like you, Nasus."

AurelionSol.tauntPantheon01.text: "Your fate was sealed the moment you picked up Targon's spear."

AurelionSol.tauntRammus01.text: "Are you burdened by your own monotony? Because I am."

AurelionSol.tauntRenekton01.text: "That whole practice of Ascension is adorably amusing, like a kitten trying to walk upright."

AurelionSol.tauntRyze01.text: "Ah, Ryze, I see you've brought paper to take notes."

AurelionSol.tauntRyze02.text: "True magic is beyond language. Writing merely butchers the intent."

AurelionSol.tauntRyze03.text: "Magic tattoos? Where did you get those, magic prison?... oh."

AurelionSol.tauntShyvana02.text: "A dragon's loyalty is a priceless gift. Do not waste it in the service of fools."

AurelionSol.tauntShyvana03.text: "Medium flame, and that is me being generous."

AurelionSol.tauntSoraka01.text: "Twinkle, twinkle, little star, do you wonder what you are?"

AurelionSol.tauntTahmKench01.text: "The heavens drag on endlessly... much like a conversation with you."

AurelionSol.tauntTargon01.text: "The Aspect of Targon? Sparks masquerading as lightning."

AurelionSol.tauntTargon02.text: "I will cauterize Targon with star fire."

AurelionSol.tauntTaric01.text: "You're an Aspect? Let me guess - tackiness."

AurelionSol.tauntTryndamere01.text: "Galaxies exist by my will - but, yes, that is certainly an impressive sword."

AurelionSol.tauntVi02.text: "You are going to punch a star dragon. Good luck with that."

AurelionSol.tauntZac01.text: "I empathize with your life as a weapon, but have a little backbone."

AurelionSol.tauntZilean01.text: "You bend time the way a child folds origami - cute, but nothing special."

AurelionSol.joke01.text: "Few can impress me. That is a compliment."

AurelionSol.joke02.text: "Which star is your favorite? I made that one."

AurelionSol.joke03.text: "I made the stars... but you inspire me to make more."

AurelionSol.joke04.text: "First you start with some matter, then add star fire and voila! It basically does the rest itself."

AurelionSol.joke05.text: "Runeterra? I mean the name of this world literally means 'magic earth'."

AurelionSol.joke06.text: "I made the stars to illuminate the perpetual nothing, and mortals use them for... relationship advice."

AurelionSol.joke07.text: "A sun is unimaginable celestial power - and thrilled mortals use theirs to coordinate this 'lunch time'."

AurelionSol.joke09.text: "Of course I love Runeterra! You have buildings and... more buildings."

AurelionSol.dance01.text: "Hello, Runeterra! Are you ready to rock?"

AurelionSol.spellIkill04.text: "My wish upon a star came true."

AurelionSol.spellImultikill02.text: "Stars are best viewed from a distance."
AurelionSol.spellImultikill02.trigger: Upon killing multiple enemy champions with a star

AurelionSol.spellImultikill03.text: "The stars were not in their favor."
AurelionSol.spellImultikill03.trigger: Upon killing multiple enemy champions with a star

AurelionSol.spellImultikill04.text: "I guess their fate was written in the stars."
AurelionSol.spellImultikill04.trigger: Upon killing multiple enemy champions with a star

AurelionSol.spellQ7.text: "A little dim - but it still works."

AurelionSol.spellQ9.text: "This will be quite the deadly spectacle."

AurelionSol.item01.text: "Put it on my tab. The name's Pantheon, with a P."

AurelionSol.item03.text: "Pay? Do you know who I am?"

AurelionSol.itemRodofAges01.text: "Some things are simply better with age."

AurelionSol.itemRodofAges02.text: "Ages? This thing has been around for centuries, tops."

AurelionSol.itemRodofAges03.text: "It's been around for ages? So... almost new."

AurelionSol.itemRodofAges04.text: "All things appreciate in value over time."

AurelionSol.itemRabadonsDeathcap02.text: "As long as it's set at a jaunty angle I'm in."

AurelionSol.itemOrbofWinter01.text: "A snow globe? Perfect for my collect - to destroy you. Destroy you!"

AurelionSol.itemRylaisCrystalScepter01.text: "Time to slow things down a bit."

AurelionSol.itemRylaisCrystalScepter02.text: "A bit gaudy for my tastes but exceedingly useful."

AurelionSol.itemLiandrysTorment02.text: "Perfect for the bimillenial celestial masquerade ball."

AurelionSol.itemLiandrysTorment03.text: "If Bard and Kindred can pull off wearing a mask, so can I."

AurelionSol.itemLudensEcho01.text: "There are no echoes where I'm from."

AurelionSol.tower01.text: "All towers fall - it's just what they do when I'm around."
AurelionSol.tower01.trigger: Upon an enemy tower dropping below 30% health

AurelionSol.tower02.text: "Nothing they build can endure like the celestial firmament."
AurelionSol.tower02.trigger: Upon an enemy tower dropping below 30% health

AurelionSol.tower03.text: "Towers tend to crumble when I am in the vicinity."
AurelionSol.tower03.trigger: Upon an enemy tower dropping below 30% health

AurelionSol.tower04.text: "Topple, like all things crafted by mortals."
AurelionSol.tower04.trigger: Upon an enemy tower dropping below 30% health

AurelionSol.tower05.text: "The architects of these towers misunderstand object permanence."
AurelionSol.tower05.trigger: Upon an enemy tower dropping below 30% health

AurelionSol.towerKill01.text: "How many must I knock down before they learn?"

AurelionSol.firstblood01.text: "You may look forward to more of this."

AurelionSol.ace01.text: "Never stop when you're on a roll."

AurelionSol.ace02.text: "I shall inscribe this moment in the stars."

AurelionSol.pentakill01.text: "That ought to keep them talking for the next century or so."

AurelionSol.pentakill02.text: "Cosmic dragon; five. Everyone else; zero. Please, take notes."

AurelionSol.recall04.text: "Always know when to make an entrance - and an exit."

AurelionSol.death01.text: "Alas, I am simply too beautiful for this world."

AurelionSol.death04.text: "The brightest stars shine on long after they're gone."

AurelionSol.deathShyvana01.text: "Darling, you have but set my hearts free."
AurelionSol.deathShyvana01.trigger: Upon being killed by an enemy Shyvana

AurelionSol.shutdown01.text: "With a lifespan as comically brief as yours, I suppose I can allow you to taste triumph at least once."

AurelionSol.shutdown02.text: "Ah, the joys of lesser organisms rising up to slay their betters! If only they were aware of the impermanence of being... or the permanence of me."

AurelionSol.respawn02.text: "Because I am a star dragon. That's why."

AurelionSol.respawn03.text: "It's not a comeback if one was never truly gone."

Zac.attack05.text: "These jerks don't know when to quit!"

Zac.attack13.text: "Beat up, or beat down? I'm flexible."

Zac.move06.text: "I'm not as squishy as I look."

Zac.move07.text: "Fighting is in my blood... I mean... my goo."

Zac.move08.text: "I may bend, but I don't break."

Zac.move09.text: "Mom always said I was big for my age."

Zac.move10.text: "There's plenty of me to go around."

Zac.move11.text: "I could really use a snack right now."

Zac.taunt01.text: "It's not how much you can lift. It's how good you look!"

Yasuo.move01.text: "A sword's poor company for a long road."

Yasuo.move02.text: "My honor left a long time ago."

Yasuo.move04.text: "Follow the wind, but watch your back."

Yasuo.move06.text: "Virtue is no more than a luxury."

Yasuo.move07.text: "The road to ruin is shorter than you think."

Yasuo.move10.text: "Hmph. One step ahead of the past."

Yasuo.move14.text: "I will follow this path until the end."

Yasuo.move15.text: "Honor is in the heart, not the name."

Yasuo.move16.text: "I will not forget who I am."

Yasuo.move18.text: "Is a leaf's only purpose to fall?"

Yasuo.attack02.text: "I'll give you the easy way out."

Yasuo.attack08.text: "At peace with yourself? You will be."

Yasuo.attack15.text: "It is not yet time to die."

Yasuo.joke01.text: "The blade above all things... except a good drink."

Yasuo.joke02.text: "Who says I can't handle my drink?"

Yasuo.joke03.text: "There are three certainties in life: honor, death, and hangovers."

Yasuo.taunt01.text: "There is only death... mine, or yours!"

Yasuo.taunt02.text: "If you've come to kill me... I hope you brought friends."

Yasuo.taunt03.text: "Killing people is a bad habit... but I can't seem to quit."

Yasuo.Ninjataunt03.text: "Cute mask. Your, uh, mom sew that?"

Yasuo.Riventaunt01.text: "Which weighs more, Riven? Your blade, or your past?"

Yasuo.Riventaunt03.text: "You can't run from yourself, Riven... I've tried."

VelKoz.move07.text: "There is much to learn about this world."

VelKoz.move10.text: "I miss the darkness of the Void."

VelKoz.move15.text: "Genders are more easily discerned by the pitch of their cries."

VelKoz.move16.text: "To date, none have survived preliminary testing."

VelKoz.move19.text: "Ah, the Void. I miss the darkness."

VelKoz.attack11.text: "Creature appears to seek its maternal unit."

VelKoz.attack21.text: "Flailing appears to be a universal response."

VelKoz.attack22.text: "They possess a variety of internal aromas."

VelKoz.taunt01.text: "It seems your chances of survival are... less than zero."

VelKoz.taunt02.text: "Let's see... yes, infinity more samples required!"

Taliyah.startSummonersRift02.text: "A bird's trust is not in the branch."

Taliyah.startSummonersRift04.text: "Every tapestry begins with a single stitch."

Taliyah.startTwistedTreeline01.text: "The ground here conceals a mighty power."

Taliyah.startCrystalScar01.text: "The wounds of this land run deep."

Taliyah.attack01.text: "Looks like you're stuck between me and a hard place."

Taliyah.attack02.text: "Our paths have woven together for a reason."

Taliyah.attack05.text: "I've given up too much to let you stop me."

Taliyah.attack06.text: "Mastery is a journey. Here's your first lesson."

Taliyah.attack07.text: "Okay, great, that is actually what I wanted to have happen. For once."

Taliyah.attack08.text: "My father always said I was a shepherd's nightmare."

Taliyah.attack09.text: "It will take more than you to break me."

Taliyah.attack20.text: "A rock in my hand is worth two in your face!"

Taliyah.attack24.text: "Either way, I'm going to learn something from this."

Taliyah.attack25.text: "Looks like you've got a thing or two to learn yourself."

Taliyah.attack29.text: "Every rock tells a story. This one might be painful."

Taliyah.attack36.text: "I am the stone beneath your feet."

Taliyah.attack38.text: "The best defense is a strong foundation."

Taliyah.attackJungle01.trigger: Upon Attacking an Enemy in the Jungle

Taliyah.attackRiver01.text: "I'm the rock the river cannot wash away!"
Taliyah.attackRiver01.trigger: Upon Attacking an Enemy in the River

Taliyah.interactionEnemyEscape01.trigger: When an Enemy Gets Away with Low Health

Taliyah.firstBloodEnemy01.text: (Enemy) "A stone can't be polished without a little friction."

Taliyah.spreeKillingSpree01.text: "Great, now who am I going to learn from?"
Taliyah.spreeKillingSpree01.trigger: Upon Going on a Killing Spree

Taliyah.tower01.text: "That... was... amazing! Let us see if I can do it again!"

Taliyah.tower02.text: "Some walls were meant to come down."

Taliyah.attackBaron02.text: "As before, we will stand against you."

Taliyah.attackDragon01.text: "Your fire is nothing compared to the desert heat."

Taliyah.attackDragon02.text: "I looked for your kind at the ends of the earth."

Taliyah.attackVilemaw02.text: "My weave is made of sturdier stuff."

Taliyah.move04.text: "A great Weaver says every lesson is a gift."

Taliyah.move07.text: "The desert's beauty lies beneath the sand."

Taliyah.move09.text: "Keep your eyes on the horizon and your feet on the ground."

Taliyah.move10.text: "My journey is not yet at an end."

Taliyah.move11.text: "A tribe without tradition is a flock without a shepherd."

Taliyah.move12.text: "It is up to all of us to see beauty in the bare stone."

Taliyah.move13.text: "Distance means so little when family means so much."

Taliyah.move14.text: "The earth calls, and I must answer."

Taliyah.move15.text: "To conquer our fears, we must move forward."

Taliyah.move16.text: "So long as the desert blooms, there is hope."

Taliyah.move19.text: "True learning is just a stone's throw away."

Taliyah.move20.text: "Oh, look, a rock... and another... and another!"

Taliyah.move21.text: "I know all of this will lead me home someday."

Taliyah.move23.text: "This world is a tapestry of our own making."

Taliyah.move27.text: "I keep moving, but my feet are on solid ground."

Taliyah.move28.text: "If I stumble, I have the earth to catch me."

Taliyah.move29.text: "The world is my loom, and every stone my thread."

Taliyah.move30.text: "This world is frayed, and in need of mending."

Taliyah.move32.text: "I think I've learned what I need to here."

Taliyah.move33.text: "I must push myself harder next time."

Taliyah.move34.text: "The warmth of the desert calls me home."

Taliyah.moveIdle01.text: "Just when I start to appreciate the view, it is time to move on."
Taliyah.moveIdle01.trigger: Upon Moving After Speaking an Idle Phrase

Taliyah.taunt01.text: "Maybe I'm here to teach you something."

Taliyah.taunt02.text: "You're never too old to learn something new."

Taliyah.taunt03.text: "Go ahead, push me. We'll both find out what I'm made of."

Taliyah.taunt04.text: "You're not a problem, you're a learning opportunity."

Taliyah.tauntIonian01.text: (Ally) "The mountains of Ionia taught me much."

Taliyah.tauntJhin01.text: "You're no artist, just a hired gun!"

Taliyah.tauntJhin02.text: "Beauty is no excuse for so much suffering."

Taliyah.tauntYasuo03.text: "I've learned much since we last met."

Taliyah.tauntYasuo04.text: "Let me show you what I've learned."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian01.text: "The promises of Noxus are nothing but lies."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian02.text: "I will take no part in your war machine."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian03.text: "You are nothing but plunderers and poachers."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian04.text: "We will not trade the yoke of one empire for another."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian05.text: "The earth will rip itself apart before it falls to Noxus."

Taliyah.tauntNoxian06.text: "Noxus promised learning, but delivered only bloodshed."

Taliyah.tauntCassiopeia01.text: "The sands have revealed your true form."

Taliyah.tauntCassiopeia03.text: "This is how the desert repays thieves."

Taliyah.tauntCassiopeia04.text: "Noxians... why did it have to be Noxians?"

Taliyah.tauntChoGath01.text: "You are the scourge upon our world."

Taliyah.tauntKassadin02.text: "Tell us what we need to stand against those creatures."

Taliyah.tauntMalzahar01.text: "You have betrayed our people to chaos."

Taliyah.tauntMalzahar02.text: "The stone of Shurima will stand against those creatures."

Taliyah.tauntRekSai01.text: "You will stalk the sands no more."

Taliyah.tauntRekSai02.text: "You breed chaos like a rabid ralsiji!"

Taliyah.tauntVelKoz02.text: "Want to examine some stone up close?"

Taliyah.tauntVelKoz03.text: "How's that for dirt in your eye?"

Taliyah.tauntAnnie01.text: "Playtime is going to get a little rocky."

Taliyah.tauntAurelionSol01.text: "Even the smallest stone can shake the heavens."

Taliyah.tauntAzir01.text: "Remember there is stone beneath your sand."

Taliyah.tauntAzir04.text: "There is no empire without the people."

Taliyah.tauntAzir05.text: "Close to the ground, the sparrow flies faster than the falcon."

Taliyah.tauntAzir07.text: "Better to build on stone than sand."

Taliyah.tauntAzir09.text: "Shouldn't you be home polishing your Sun Disc?"

Taliyah.tauntEkko01.text: "Did the earth move for you too? Did I just say that out loud?"

Taliyah.tauntIllaoi01.text: "Don't worry. I don't stay in one place for long."

Taliyah.tauntKindred01.text: "Life and death are two ends of the same thread."

Taliyah.tauntMalphite03.text: (Enemy) "Even rock gives under the right pressure."

Taliyah.tauntNasus01.text: "Our future is not yet off the loom."

Taliyah.tauntNasus02.text: "Worry is a heavier burden than stone."

Taliyah.tauntNasus03.text: "Do not give up before the journey is finished."

Taliyah.tauntNasus04.text: "Even the most barren desert blooms in time."

Taliyah.tauntRenekton02.text: "Stone sealed your tomb once. It will again."

Taliyah.tauntRenekton03.text: "I will mend what you have sundered."

Taliyah.tauntSivir01.text: "He may be your blood, but we are your people."

Taliyah.tauntSivir03.text: "Do not turn your back on what is right."

Taliyah.tauntSkarner01.text: "I feel your tribe sleeping below the earth."

Taliyah.tauntSkarner02.text: "Is it hard to be the protector of so many?"

Taliyah.tauntSkarner03.text: "I know the power that lies beneath."

Taliyah.tauntTaric01.text: "Ooh, you're pretty. Guys can be pretty, right?"

Taliyah.tauntWarwick01.text: "It is the shepherd's duty to drive the wolf away."

Taliyah.tauntWarwick02.text: "You are nothing but a sheep in wolf's clothes."

Taliyah.tauntXerath01.text: "Yours is the ill wind that begat his wrath."

Braum.start01.text: "Good times, good friends... what could be better?"

Braum.start02.text: "If they insist on a fight, I will oblige them."

Braum.start03.text: "Ah! We are about to begin the fighting!"

Braum.start04.text: "Now, what can we learn from fighting?"

Braum.start11.text: "They may have many, but you have me."

Braum.attack01.text: "Why not enjoy some warm milk instead?"

Braum.attack05.text: "When going gets tough, you call Braum."

Braum.attack08.text: "You hit like baby ram! No horns yet!"

Braum.attack09.text: "Now I give more than harsh talking to!"

Braum.attack17.text: "Today we fight each other. Tomorrow, we may fight together."

Braum.move01.text: "Sometimes icy heart just needs warm smile."

Braum.move07.text: "If you have problem, you come to me first."

Braum.move09.text: "The darker the night, the brighter the stars."

Braum.taunt01.text: "If at first you do not succeed, please, tell me what it is like."

Braum.taunt02.text: "Don't worry, Braum was trying little bit."

Braum.tauntAlistar01.text: "You remind me of Agatha. Best cow back home."

Braum.tauntAlistar02.text: "Alistar! I have cow you should meet."

Braum.tauntAnnie01.text: "Mother gave me bear as child too, Annie."

Braum.tauntGragas01.text: "After this, we share a drink! You like goat's milk?"

Braum.tauntVi01.text: "Your hair... we do not see things like this in the Freljord."
Braum.tauntVi01.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Jinx or Vi

Braum.joke01.text: "When life gives you curdled milk, be patient. You get very good cheese!"

Braum.joke02.text: "The goats are wise; eat everything, climb everything, and if something kicks you, kick it back!"

Braum.joke03.text: "Mother always said - float like iceberg, sting like thrown iceberg!"

Braum.caitlyzreal01.text: "Good shot! You'll get them next time."
Braum.caitlyzreal01.trigger: Upon Blocking Ace in the Hole or Trueshot Barrage

Braum.poro02.text: "Train hard, little poro, and one day you will be strong like... baby!"

Braum.coin01.text: "This has the smell of a faraway land. Perhaps I shall see it one day."

Braum.sightstone01.text: "No sneaking up on Braum this time."

Braum.sightstone02.text: "Sight is the key to victory. Also stone."

Braum.frozenHeart01.text: "To friends, I am snowfall. To enemies, I am avalanche!"

Braum.randuins02.text: "A shield for my shield? I like it!"

Jhin.start03.text: "I suppose I must make do with this tawdry setting."

Jhin.start04.text: "This stage is beneath my talent, but I shall elevate it."

Jhin.start05.text: "I will bring them an opera of death."

Jhin.attack05.text: "Your life had no value before me."

Jhin.attack29.text: "When they find you, they will cry."

Jhin.attack37.text: "There is no drama in a peaceful death!"

Jhin.move03.text: "The end is important in all things."

Jhin.move05.text: "I must wait until a composition is perfect."

Jhin.move06.text: "They're puppets. I pull their strings, and then they dance."

Jhin.move09.text: "They call me mad. All artists are mad."

Jhin.move11.text: "I cannot be good. I must be perfection."

Jhin.move15.text: "It's so difficult to work under these conditions."

Jhin.move17.text: "I am at my best only during the performance."

Jhin.move18.text: "I am pure. My work is pure."

Jhin.move21.text: "No poet's words could match my craft."

Jhin.move22.text: "Death should never be quick. It should be an opera."

Jhin.move25.text: "The world is cruel. It does not have to be ugly."

Jhin.move26.text: "Everyone wears a mask. I just chose to create my own."

Jhin.move27.text: "This art is a compulsion. I cannot resist it."

Jhin.move30.text: "There is nothing for me but this."

Jhin.move31.text: "I never hurt anyone. It is the performance that kills."

Jhin.move32.text: "Until they stop me, I will keep going."

Jhin.move33.text: "I am the singer without a voice. The dancer without legs."

Jhin.move34.text: "Only to the audience do I show my true face."

Jhin.move35.text: "Each bullet is a piece of my soul. Each shot is a piece of me."

Jhin.move36.text: "I swear each performance is the last, but I lie every time."

Jhin.move37.text: "I am a slave to this passion."

Jhin.move38.text: "My work asks questions, it never has answers."

Jhin.move39.text: "Which is the lie? The mask, or my face?"

Jhin.move40.text: "An icon doesn't have to explain himself."

Jhin.move41.text: "I wonder what they think when they see me."

Jhin.move44.text: "This would be easier if blood came in more colours."

Jhin.move48.text: "If I keep getting interrupted, how can I be expected to work?"

Jhin.move49.text: "I was paid to put on a killer show."

Jhin.move51.text: "They will dance, they will sing, they will die!"

Jhin.move52.text: "A costume, some makeup, a spray of blood."

Jhin.move53.text: "It's very simple - when I shoot, they dance."

Jhin.move55.text: "If I get this outfit dirty, I'm going to be so annoyed."

Jhin.move57.text: "Death is certain, but killing doesn't have to be ugly."

Jhin.move58.text: "I provide catharsis for my clients, and my victims."

Jhin.move60.text: "I get nervous before every performance, but I need that feeling."

Jhin.move61.text: "The moment before the shot... is painful."

Jhin.move62.text: "It is only when the gun fires that I am alive."

Jhin.move64.text: "The trigger on a loaded weapon... it whispers for us to act."

Jhin.move65.text: "I can't live without the euphoria of performance."

Jhin.move67.text: "I want to feel everything. The gun makes it so I do."

Jhin.move68.text: "I envy silence... because I must be loud."

Jhin.taunt03.text: "Killing you will be one of my finest works."

Jhin.taunt04.text: "You are mediocrity. My genius will supplant you."

Jhin.taunt05.text: "Only my actions will make you memorable."

Jhin.tauntIonian01.text: "You only understand harmony. Discord is required for contrast."

Jhin.tauntIonian02.text: "My dear countryman, you remind me how little our culture has advanced."

Jhin.tauntIonian03.text: "I am avant-garde - you are stuck in the past."

Jhin.tauntIonian04.text: "The Noxian invasion should be a wake-up call. We need more elaborate productions."

Jhin.tauntIonian05.text: "I do what others will not. That alone is innovation."

Jhin.tauntShen01.text: "I remember your father! He thought he could censor me."

Jhin.tauntShen02.text: "I have been planning your final performance for a very... long... time."

Jhin.tauntShen03.text: "You helped lock me away. You tried to stop my work. My art cannot be contained."

Jhin.tauntShen04.text: "Your father was a merciful man. Only his failure will be remembered."

Jhin.tauntShen05.text: "Your father's death denied me a performance. You will be his stand-in."

Jhin.tauntZed01.text: "You wanted to kill me back then, didn't you? You will learn - art cannot be killed."

Jhin.tauntZed02.text: "You think you can stop my performance?"

Jhin.tauntZed04.text: "I remember your master. He was worth remembering."

Jhin.tauntZed05.text: "You were wrong to kill your master. I needed him for this performance."

Jhin.tauntZed06.text: "You belong in the shadows. No audience could love you."

Jhin.tauntZed07.text: "I offer an exclusive service. You'll find I murder the competition."

Jhin.tauntNoxian01.text: "I've been asked to do so many boring performances in your nation."

Jhin.tauntNoxian03.text: "Noxians treat killing as a sport. It is an art."

Jhin.tauntNoxian05.text: "Your war was an impressive production, but it lacked soul."

Jhin.tauntDraven01.text: "You shout and throw machetes? How quaint."

Jhin.tauntDraven03.text: "I find your work very, very... obvious."

Jhin.tauntBard01.text: "Wait for your cue! You're only here to herald my entrance."

Jhin.tauntIllaoi01.text: "When you speak, I don't hear god, I hear an idiot babbling."

Jhin.tauntIllaoi02.text: "Here's the thing, I don't need your god, I need more time for my production."

Jhin.tauntIllaoi03.text: "You can take my soul... if you'll shut up."

Jhin.tauntIllaoi04.text: "There is such a thing as 'too much gold', my dear."

Jhin.tauntIllaoi05.text: "I thought diamonds were a girl's best friend."

Jhin.tauntJinx01.text: "So many guns, all lacking in meaning or artistry."

Jhin.tauntLucian01.text: "Your story is revenge with guns and ghosts. How droll."

Jhin.tauntRekSai01.text: "I suppose you embody a primitive minimalism, but you lack my technique."

Jhin.tauntSion01.text: "Break a leg! Hehe, oh. 'Break a leg', hehe... ah, delightful. I do cut myself up."

Jhin.tauntSona01.text: "Your music lacks the cruelty of a masterpiece."

Jhin.tauntSona02.text: "You should learn the power of silence."

Jhin.tauntSona03.text: "Step out of my light! They call it background music!"

Jhin.tauntSona04.text: "Your work will be forgotten. I am ahead of my time!"

Jhin.tauntTahmKench01.text: "How inelegant your words are. Surely a fool wrote your script."

Jhin.tauntTahmKench03.text: "Why would anyone listen to a creature so ugly?"

Jhin.tauntTahmKench04.text: "Heh... hehe... that hat is ridiculous, now... who let you wear that horrible thing?"

Jhin.tauntTahmKench05.text: "Oh, before you ask, yes, your whole ensemble makes you look fat. Very fat."

Jhin.joke01.text: "Only perfectio - gah! ... only perfection is acceptable."

Jhin.I11.text: "You will learn what beauty truly is."
Jhin.I11.trigger: While Whisper's Fourth Shot is Loaded

Jhin.E1.text: "Now that is what I want to see."
Jhin.E1.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E2.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E3.text: "Life has no meaning, but your death shall."
Jhin.E3.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E4.text: "I live for the applause, you will die for it."
Jhin.E4.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E5.text: "I knew you would find your mark, eventually."
Jhin.E5.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E6.trigger: When a Champion Steps on a Lotus Trap

Jhin.E7.text: "Face the crowd, and bleed for them."

Jhin.itemBansheesVeil01.text: "I love to perform, but I hate crowds."

Jhin.itemBerserkersGreaves01.text: "These were clearly designed by a caveman."

Jhin.itemEssenceReaver01.text: "The essence of a thing is found only in its absence."

Jhin.itemHauntingGuise01.text: "We all wear masks. Mine are just better-crafted."

Jhin.itemLastWhisper02.text: "I prefer my equipment to make a bang."

Jhin.itemLiandrysTorment01.text: "Not sure I needed another mask, but oh well."

Jhin.itemPhantomDancer01.text: "Start the music. I will make them dance."

Jhin.itemRapidFirecannon01.text: "Rapid fire? Huh. Where's the drama in that?"

Jhin.itemRunaansHurricane01.text: "The storm is in their hearts. I calm them."

Jhin.itemStatikkShiv01.text: "It is by my will alone I set my mind in motion."

Jhin.itemStatikkShiv02.text: "I do prefer my work to have a brisk tempo."

Jhin.move69.text: "In carnage, I bloom, like a flower in the dawn."

Jhin.move70.text: "I have risen from the filth and muck. I am the lotus blossom. I am beauty."

Jhin.move71.text: "That delightful moment before the curtain goes up."

Kindred.start01.text:
Wolf: "Never one..."
 Lamb: "... without the other."

Kindred.start02.text:
Lamb: "Never one..."
 Wolf: "... without the other."

Kindred.start03.text:
Lamb: "Every life..."
 Wolf: "... ends with us."

Kindred.start04.text:
Wolf: "Tell me again, little Lamb, which things are mine to take?"
 Lamb: "All things, dear Wolf."

Kindred.attack08.text: Lamb: "How one dies shows how one lived."

Kindred.attack22.text:
Lamb: "Life is ours..."
 Wolf: "... to end!"

Kindred.attack26.text:
Lamb: "Flee - or stand firm."
 Wolf: "Doesn't matter!"

Kindred.attack27.text:
Lamb: "Day always turns to..."
 Wolf: "... food!"

Kindred.move01.text: Lamb: "Those who dread us grant us the most power."

Kindred.move02.text: Lamb: "We are not dreams. We are the waking."

Kindred.move03.text: Lamb: "The only true death is to never live.

Kindred.move04.text: Lamb: "There are so many ways to die.

Kindred.move05.text: Lamb: "Those who run from death... stood still in life.

Kindred.move06.text: Lamb: "All will know us... in time.

Kindred.move07.text: Lamb: "Beauty fades. That is why it is beautiful."

Kindred.move08.text: Lamb: "Wolf chases what does not willingly go."

Kindred.move09.text: Lamb: "Tomorrow is a hope, never a promise."

Kindred.move14.text: Wolf: "Bits of them stick in my claws!"

Kindred.move15.text: Wolf: "Fear makes the chase more fun!"

Kindred.move17.text: Wolf: "Can't wait for them to flee!"

Kindred.move19.text:
Lamb: "How does hunger feel?"
 Wolf: "Always there."

Kindred.move20.text:
Lamb: "I wonder how they see me."
 Wolf: "Ashes on wool."

Kindred.move21.text:
Wolf: "What sound do they make?"
 Lamb: "Feathers falling on fresh snow."

Kindred.move22.text:
Wolf: "None can hide!"
 Lamb: "Though many try."

Kindred.move23.text:
Wolf: "They race from us!"
 Lamb: "Only to find us sooner."

Kindred.move24.text:
Lamb: "The weft and weave of fate guides-"
 Wolf: "Words spoil the chase!"

Kindred.move25.text:
Lamb: "All things linger..."
 Wolf: "... in our shadow."

Kindred.move26.text:
Wolf: "They know we'll come."
 Lamb: "Yet they are never prepared."

Kindred.move27.text:
Wolf: "How long will we be together?"
 Lamb: "Forever more."

Kindred.move28.text:
Lamb: "Peacefully, they go."
 Wolf: "Hungry, we follow!"

Kindred.move29.text:
Lamb: "They laugh."
 Wolf: "And scream!"
 Lamb: "And dance."
 Wolf: "And flee!"

Kindred.move30.text:
Wolf: "And everywhere Lamb went..."
 Lamb: "... Wolf was sure to follow."

Kindred.move31.text:
Lamb: "And everywhere Lamb went..."
 Wolf: "Wolf was sure to follow!"

Kindred.taunt01.text:
Wolf: "I see water!"
 Lamb: "They're called... tears."

Kindred.taunt02.text: Wolf: "Chasing is the best game in the world... and I always win!"

Kindred.taunt03.text:
Wolf: "I'll give you a running start!"
 Lamb: "Not that it will help."

Kindred.taunt04.text:
Wolf: "It thinks it can beat us!"
 Lamb: "This is called... denial."

Kindred.taunt05.text:
Lamb: "Choose now - my arrows..."
 Wolf: "... or my teeth?!"

Kindred.tauntAmumu01.text:
Lamb: "We understand your loneliness, but..."
 Wolf: "Stay away!"

Kindred.tauntEkko01.text: Lamb: "We know your name child. Woven across countless almost-lives."

Kindred.tauntUnknown01.text: Lamb: "Rushing to meet us again, I see."

Kindred.tauntKarthus01.text:
Wolf: "His song sounds good."
 Lamb: "The singer mistakes melody for substance."

Kindred.tauntUnknown03.text:
Lamb: "Long have we shadowed your deeds."
 Wolf: "Turn and face us now!"

Kindred.tauntRengar02.text:
Lamb: "Rengar is well-versed in the ways of the hunter."
 Wolf: "Now, he's prey!"

Kindred.tauntSion01.text: Lamb: "Come, Sion, let us end this mockery."

Kindred.tauntWarwick01.text: Wolf: "There are no wolves like me!"

Kindred.joke01.text:
Lamb: "Hold still, Wolf."
 Wolf: "Ahh! Don't shoot me!"

Kindred.joke02.text:
Wolf: "What happens if you miss?"
 Lamb: "I don't know."

Kindred.joke03.text:
Wolf: "Words, words, la la la, pew twang pew!"
 Lamb: "Are you imitating me?"

Kindred.joke04.text:
Lamb: "I'm hungry, I'm hungry, I'm bored, chase chase chase!"
 Wolf: "You get it now!"

Kindred.joke05.text: Lamb: "The weft and weave of fate guides... um... uh... how did that poem go again?"

Kindred.mark01.text: Kindred: "The masks of the Kindred seek you!"

Kindred.mark14.text: Lamb: "A fine life reaches its conclusion."

Kindred.mark20.text: Lamb: "Their path is destined to cross ours."

Kindred.mark15.text: Wolf: "I hope this one has strong legs!"

Kindred.mark16.text: Wolf: "I will chase it until it's dead!"

Kindred.mark02.text:
Lamb: "We have your name."
 Wolf: "And your scent!"

Kindred.mark04.text:
Lamb: "Your time has come."
 Wolf: "Ready or not!"

Kindred.mark11.text:
Wolf: "We know your name!"
 Lamb: "We have always known it."

Kindred.mark13.text:
Lamb: "When you see us..."
 Wolf: "... it's too late!"

Kindred.mark18.text:
Lamb: "Shall we, dear Wolf?"
 Wolf: "Race you there!"

Kindred.mark19.text:
Wolf: "This next one will be easy."
 Lamb: "And if not?"
 Wolf: "More fun."

Kindred.mark21.text:
Wolf: Its heart beats fast now!"
 Lamb: "It knows."

Kindred.markKill05.text: Lamb: "Such befalls all who bear our mark."

Kindred.markKill09.text: Lamb: "All your life has led to this moment."

Kindred.markKill01.text:
Wolf: "We take our mark!"
 Lamb: "Only to place it elsewhere."

Kindred.markKill02.text:
Lamb: "Our mark is lifted."
 Wolf: "Who's next?!"

Kindred.markKill04.text:
Wolf: "No match for me!"
 Lamb: "None are, dear Wolf."

Kindred.markKill11.text:
Lamb: "All things, great and small..."
 Wolf: "... die."

Kindred.markKill13.text:
Wolf: "No match for us!"
 Lamb: "Few are, dear Wolf."

Kindred.markKill14.text:
Wolf: "The chase ends!"
 Lamb: "More lie ahead, dear Wolf."

Kindred.markKill16.text:
Lamb: "If it draws breath..."
 Wolf: "... it meets us."

Kindred.markKill18.text:
Lamb: "The weft and weave of fate guides-"
 Wolf: "The hunt is back on!"

Kindred.markSteal03.text: Lamb: "That was meant to be ours."

Kindred.markSteal04.trigger: When a hunted monster dies to an enemy champion

Kindred.markSteal05.text: Lamb: "What folly it is to snatch our marks."
Kindred.markSteal05.trigger: When a hunted monster dies to an enemy champion

Kindred.markSteal07.trigger: When a hunted monster dies to an enemy champion

Kindred.markSteal01.trigger: When a hunted monster dies to an enemy champion

Kindred.markSteal02.trigger: When a hunted monster dies to an enemy champion

Kindred.markSteal08.trigger: When a hunted monster dies to an enemy champion

Kindred.markSteal06.text:
Lamb: "An emboldened thief."
 Wolf: "I will eat it!"
Kindred.markSteal06.trigger: When a hunted monster dies to an enemy champion

Kindred.markSteal09.text:
Lamb: "You steal from us..."
 Wolf: "We steal from you."
Kindred.markSteal09.trigger: When a hunted monster dies to an enemy champion

Kindred.W2.text:
Wolf: "My turn!"
 Lamb: "Chase to your heart's content."

Kindred.itemInfinityEdge02.text: Lamb: "Sharp enough to slice the veil between life and death."

Kindred.itemInfinityEdge03.text: Lamb: "A sharper blade makes for a cleaner death."

Kindred.itemLastWhisper01.text: Lamb: "They shall only hear my voice."

Kindred.itemLastWhisper03.text:
Lamb: "Strip away their armor."
 Wolf: "Rip it to shreds!"

Kindred.itemBloodthirster03.text: Lamb: "They shall not ignore us so easily."

Kindred.itemBotRK01.text: Lamb: "Forged in a land unwelcome to us."
Kindred.itemBotRK01.trigger: Upon buying Blade of the Ruined King

Kindred.unknown02.text:
Wolf: "Lamb, tell me a story."
 Lamb: "There was once a pale man with dark hair who was very lonely."
 Wolf: "Why was it lonely?"
 Lamb: "All things must meet this man, so they shunned him."
 Wolf: "Did he chase them all?"
 Lamb: "He took an axe and split himself in two right down the middle."
 Wolf: "So he would always have a friend?"
 Lamb: "So he would always have a friend."

Kindred.unknown01.text:
Lamb: "Are you there, dear Wolf?"
 Wolf: "I am, little Lamb."
 Lamb: "Are you sad?"
 Wolf: "I am."
 Lamb: "What does it feel like?"
 Wolf: "A long hunt with no kill."

Kindred.unknown03.text:
Wolf: "Is it time?"
 Lamb: "We will soon awaken from this pale slumber."

Kindred.unknown04.text:
Wolf: "Is this what it feels like to end?"
 Lamb: "I do not know, for this is not our end."
 Wolf: "Do others come back?"
 Lamb: "Those who do, wish they hadn't."

Kindred.unknown05.text:
Wolf: "How old are we, Lamb?"
 Lamb: "Older than those whose footsteps are long vanished."
 Wolf: "Many years."
 Lamb: "I remember them all."

MafiaJinx.attack02.text: "I've got a recital, and everyone's invited!"

Jinx.move01.text: "Let's just behave... said no one, ever."

Jinx.move02.text: "Wait, I'm thinking! Urgh... how do people do this?"

Jinx.move03.text: "I'm trying to care but I just can't!"

Jinx.move06.text: "Now where was I? Oh, right, wreaking havoc!"

Jinx.move07.text: "Hold on! I'm about to say something really cool!"

Jinx.move08.text: "Ask me if I'm listening! Hint: I'm not!"

Jinx.move09.text: "I don't even think once about blowing stuff up!"

Jinx.move10.text: "'She's such a loser, always ready to cry!' T-t-t-ta!"

Jinx.move11.text: "You think I'm crazy? You should see my sister!"'

Jinx.move13.text: "I'm wearing lots of belts! For no reason at all."

Jinx.move17.text: "All part of the plan I just made up!"

Jinx.move18.text: "What if I had a gun that... shot other guns?"

Jinx.move19.text: "Aww, c'mon, what's the worst that could happen?"

Jinx.move21.text: "I really need a new gun. But don't tell my other guns."

Jinx.taunt01.text: "Guns don't kill people. I mean, until you shoot them. Then they kill everything!"

Jinx.taunt02.text: "I'm bringing guns to the knife fight! Hehe."

Jinx.taunt03.text: "Say hello to my friends of varying sizes!"

Jinx.taunt04.text: "Three guns means never having to say 'I'm sorry'."

Jinx.Caitlyntaunt01.text: "Welcome to Snoresville, hat lady! Population: you."

Jinx.Caitlyntaunt02.text: "But where are your other guns, hat lady?"

Jinx.joke01.text: "Hey Fishbones, should we blow something up? 'You might inconvenience people and hurt their feelings.' You're the worst weapon ever!"

Jinx.joke02.text: "Fishbones, you know what we oughta' do? 'Do the laundry, wash dishes and pay some bills.' Stupid dumb rocket launcher."

Jinx.joke03.text: "Hey Fishbones, think we can wreak havoc forever? 'No, you should buy a home and save for retirement.' You know I can replace you, right?"

Jinx.joke04.text: "Maybe we should settle down and live peaceful lives. 'Really? I always hoped one day you'd-' Haha, nope! You're a death machine for life!"

TahmKench.taunt01.text: "You are a malodorous offense to my palate!"

TahmKench.taunt02.text: "The baseness of your appetite repulses me!"

TahmKench.taunt03.text: "Your mind is as clear as mud."

TahmKench.taunt04.text: "Child, you're a couple cows short of a steak!"

TahmKench.tauntAatrox01.text: (Enemy) "Brother, you're as cultured as a crematorium selling barbecue."

TahmKench.tauntAatrox02.text: (Ally) "War is a manly appetite, and your directness has my admiration."

TahmKench.tauntAhri01.text: (Enemy) "You're as modest as a freshly-paid courtesan."

TahmKench.tauntAhri02.text: (Ally) "I am enthralled by your class and refinement - I must offer you a token of my admirations."

TahmKench.tauntAkali01.text: (Enemy) "Hiding in smoke? Young lady, you're as sharp as a bag of slugs."

TahmKench.tauntAlistar02.text: (Ally) "Any pejorative of bullheadedness is pulverized by your magnificence."

TahmKench.tauntAmumu01.text: (Enemy) "I say, you're as 'fun' as a leaky roof."

TahmKench.tauntAmumu02.text: (Ally) "Coveting friendship is barely an appetite - but one I do so sympathize with."

TahmKench.tauntAnivia01.text: (Enemy) "I suppose I must defrost you first."

TahmKench.tauntAshe01.text: (Enemy) "Girl, you got as much 'foresight' as a blindfolded mole."

TahmKench.tauntAshe02.text: (Ally) "If you wanna' build an empire of peace, then your mortar will be blood."

TahmKench.tauntAzir01.text: (Enemy) "An emperor as humble as he is beloved."

TahmKench.tauntAzir02.text: (Enemy) "Son, your empire was built on sand."

TahmKench.tauntAzir03.text: (Enemy) "You're the emperor - of mashed potatoes and gravy."

TahmKench.tauntAzir04.text: (Enemy) "Your empire? I look upon your works and despair."

TahmKench.tauntBlitzcrank01.text: (Enemy) "If your heart is gold and your body is steel, why's tin between your ears?"

TahmKench.tauntBraum01.text: (Enemy) "You're strong like bull, and smart like cow."

TahmKench.tauntBraum03.text: (Ally) "The heart of the Freljord must long for something."

TahmKench.tauntCaitlyn01.text: (Enemy) "You're as elegant as an outhouse in a leper colony!"

TahmKench.tauntCaitlyn02.text: (Ally) "If you want to clean up the city, don't you need to understand where that dirt comes from?"

TahmKench.tauntChoGath01.text: (Enemy) "Personally I hunger for things less literal."

TahmKench.tauntDarius01.text: (Enemy) "You're as subtle as a gold codpiece."

TahmKench.tauntDarius02.text: (Ally) "Your strength is waning, General. 'course, I can help you slow time's regress."

TahmKench.tauntDiana01.text: (Enemy) "Girl, you're crazier than a mouse in moonshine."

TahmKench.tauntDiana02.text: (Ally) "Vengeance is a thirst I could help you quench."

TahmKench.tauntDraven01.text: (Enemy) "At least the rumor of your vanity isn't overrated."

TahmKench.tauntDraven02.text: (Ally) "Your hunger for attention deserves to be sated."

TahmKench.tauntDraven03.text: (Ally) "I wonder - how can you receive the attention you deserve... while your brother is in the way?"

TahmKench.tauntDrMundo01.text: (Enemy) "Your diction is as exemplary as your intellect."

TahmKench.tauntDrMundo02.text: (Ally) "I can show Mundo new places to go - if he pleases."

TahmKench.tauntEkko01.text: (Enemy) "Your youthful rebellion is as tedious as your hairstyle."

TahmKench.tauntEkko02.text: (Ally) "Time is but another river - and I care not what water I swim in."

TahmKench.tauntEzreal01.text: (Enemy) "Youthful ignorance is unfortunately your best quality."

TahmKench.tauntEzreal02.text: (Ally) "Why should a hunger for adventure ever be sated?"

TahmKench.tauntFiora01.text: (Enemy) "A duel is a fight between two imbeciles... and you are the greatest."

TahmKench.tauntFiora02.text: (Ally) "An appetite for a challenge is a craving without liability."

TahmKench.tauntFizz01.text: (Ally) "Wouldn't you care to travel to your people's destination?"

TahmKench.tauntGangplank01.text: (Enemy) "Your attempt to be monstrous is as successful as your dictatorship."

TahmKench.tauntGangplank02.text: (Ally) "You're a man with troubles. I have solutions."

TahmKench.tauntGaren01.text: (Ally) "You live by a code that'll never let you get what you want. Let me take you to her."

TahmKench.tauntGnar01.text: (Enemy) "Your conversation makes as much sense as a fish in lingerie!"

TahmKench.tauntGnar02.text: (Ally) "Time is just a river, boy, let me take you back where you belong."

TahmKench.tauntGragas01.text: (Enemy) "Your tastes are as elegant as a broken latrine."

TahmKench.tauntGragas02.text: (Ally) "I admire a man of appetites - let me help you find refreshment."

TahmKench.tauntJanna01.text: (Enemy) "Girl, you're as appealing as a cake in the rain."

TahmKench.tauntJanna02.text: (Ally) "There's a storm in your heart, girl. Tell me what you hunger for."

TahmKench.tauntJarvan01.text: (Enemy) "Anything getting through that gold helmet of yours?"

TahmKench.tauntJarvan02.text: (Ally) "Only a fool wouldn't hunger for the throne. Let me help you find that seat."

TahmKench.tauntJax01.text: (Enemy) "Boy, you are a few candles short of a lantern."

TahmKench.tauntJax02.text: (Ally) "It is wonderful to be hungry for a challenge."

TahmKench.tauntJayce02.text: (Ally) "A drive for innovation? It's just a hunger for something new."

TahmKench.tauntJinx01.text: (Enemy) "Girl, if brains were dynamite, you'd be a dud."

TahmKench.tauntJinx02.text: (Ally) "An appetite for chaos? Let me feed that mayhem."

TahmKench.tauntKatarina01.text: (Ally) "Don't starve your heart, child! Let me deliver you to him."

TahmKench.tauntLeeSin01.text: (Ally) "Truth requires a journey on blind faith."

TahmKench.tauntLissandra01.text: (Enemy) "Good ideas fall from you like pudding from a harpy."

TahmKench.tauntLissandra02.text: (Ally) "Could I offer you a bargain to replace your previous engagement?"

TahmKench.tauntLucian01.text: (Enemy) "A fool and his love are easily parted."

TahmKench.tauntLucian02.text: (Ally) "Step closer, and I'll carry you to your prize."

TahmKench.tauntMissFortune02.text: (Enemy) "The enormity of the hat doesn't hide the vacancy beneath it!"

TahmKench.tauntMissFortune01.text: (Ally) "The road to vengeance requires a journey I would happily provide."

TahmKench.tauntNami02.text: (Ally) "A journey to a moonstone is one I could provide."

TahmKench.tauntNasus01.text: (Enemy) "You're like a roofless mansion - impressively useless."

TahmKench.tauntNasus02.text: (Ally) "Forgiveness is a shore like any other."

TahmKench.tauntRenekton01.text: (Enemy) "I appreciate your mind is unsullied by the complications of reason."

TahmKench.tauntRyze01.text: (Enemy) "You read words and mistake that for understanding."

TahmKench.tauntRyze02.text: (Ally) "You are a traveller... and I provide transport."

TahmKench.tauntSejuani01.text: (Enemy) "You're as witty as you are subtle."

TahmKench.tauntSejuani02.text: (Ally) "Let me make a meal with your ambition."

TahmKench.tauntSivir01.text: (Enemy) "Your tastes are about as sophisticated as your wardrobe."

TahmKench.tauntSivir02.text: (Ally) "Why not travel to when you were free from these doubts?"

TahmKench.tauntTeemo01.text: (Enemy) "You're as likable as a rat in a bridle shop."

TahmKench.tauntTeemo02.text: (Ally) "Every heart has its own hunger. Tell me yours."

TahmKench.tauntTwistedFate01.text: (Enemy) "A gambler's luck is only predictable... when he's a cheat."

TahmKench.tauntTwistedFate02.text: (Ally) "Bilgewater is a rough town to leave - I could make it easier for you."'

TahmKench.tauntVi01.text: (Enemy) "A boxer who thinks with her fists must inevitably punch with her face."

TahmKench.tauntVi02.text: (Ally) "Child, why would you sublimate a hunger? Have you forgotten who you are?"

TahmKench.tauntWukong01.text: (Ally) "Do you want to reach your potential? It's a journey I could provide."

TahmKench.tauntXerath01.text: (Enemy) "A slave's mind is never free, but I suspect you got yours on discount."

TahmKench.tauntXerath02.text: (Ally) "Ah, nothing whets my appetite like the flames of ambition gone awry."

TahmKench.tauntYasuo01.text: (Enemy) "You're as quick as a turtle on molasses."

TahmKench.tauntYasuo02.text: (Ally) "Your destiny isn't in the wind - it's on the river."

TahmKench.tauntZed01.text: (Enemy) "So, shiny attire seem like the thing to wear? You are the most intelligent ninja in the world."

TahmKench.tauntZed02.text: (Ally) "Child, a shadow must run from the light eventually."

Azir.move03.text: "The world is a desert. I am the oasis."

Azir.attack02.text: "The unworthy have no place in history."

Azir.dragon03.text: "Even dragons look up to the sun."

Azir.vilemaw01.text: "This spider will be trampled in our march."

Azir.vilemaw02.text: "You may be large, Vilemaw, but you remain an insect to me."

Azir.vilemaw03.text: "It is you who are in my web, spider."

Azir.baron03.text: "What is a baron to an emperor?"

Azir.move04.text: "The power of the sun lives in Shurima."

Azir.move05.text: "You need not follow, but you must witness."

Azir.move08.text: "My empire lives in every grain of sand."

Azir.move15.text: "We will unearth what has been lost."

Azir.move16.text: "None know the will of the desert better than I."

Azir.move18.text: "The Ascended shall guide humanity to greatness."

Azir.joke01.text: "So, a pigeon walks into a bar..."

Azir.joke02.text: "For emperors, it's all about how you carry yourself."

Azir.taunt01.text: "There is only Shurima. All else is but a mirage."

Azir.taunt02.text: "What is the desert, but the ashes of my enemies?"

Azir.taunt03.text: "When every trace of you is lost, I will remain."

Azir.tauntSivir03.text: "Rise with Shurima, Sivir, or fall beneath it."

Azir.tauntRenekton01.text: "Renekton, once a noble warrior, now naught but a mad beast."

Azir.tauntXerath01.text: "You are but a grain of sand, Xerath."

Azir.tauntXerath02.text: "Emperors have no rivals, Xerath. Only liabilities."

Azir.tauntXerath03.text: "Xerath, it is time your spark went out."

Azir.tauntXerath04.text: "You have already failed, Xerath. You must now accept it."

Azir.tauntXerath05.text: "Traitor, I cast you to the winds."

Azir.tauntXerath07.text: "Xerath, the time of your judgment has come."

Illaoi.start01.text: "It is my burden to carry an eye of god. It is my privilege to see the truth."

Illaoi.start02.text: "We cannot comprehend the design. A raindrop cannot comprehend a river valley."

Illaoi.start03.text: "To die is to drown - so I will swim well, till I can swim no more."

Illaoi.attack15.text: "Ha ha ha, you think you can beat me?"

Illaoi.attack16.text: "They need wisdom. They don't need teeth."

Illaoi.baron01.text: "I slayed greater serpents as a child."

Illaoi.baron02.text: "Here they call you a monster. In Buhru, we would call you dinner."

Illaoi.move01.text: "If I hate something, I destroy it. If I want something, I take it."

Illaoi.move02.text: "I am a teacher. Bilgewater will learn."

Illaoi.move03.text: "We are born knowing what to do. We must only act."

Illaoi.move05.text: "It is terrible to be satisfied. The world needs us to chase dreams."

Illaoi.move06.text: "This ends one of two ways - they run, or I break them."

Illaoi.move07.text: "I don't scare, I don't tire, and I don't stop."

Illaoi.move08.text: "Good? Evil? Why should we care for such things?"

Illaoi.move09.text: "Life is the sweetness of fruit, and the joy of battle!"

Illaoi.move10.text: "There is joy in food... and fighting."

Illaoi.move14.text: "Ah, everyone has a plan, until they get punched in the face."

Illaoi.move15.text: "Men live, men die. Change is good."

Illaoi.move16.text: "They will learn or they will die."

Illaoi.move17.text: "There are kind and gentle gods. Mine isn't one of those."

Illaoi.move18.text: "The ocean is calm. It is our desires that stir it."

Illaoi.move19.text: "Even if I die, I die in motion."

Illaoi.move20.text: "The waves will drag you down, unless you fight to shore."

Illaoi.move21.text: "How could I love only one man? They break too easily."

Illaoi.move23.text: "Wisdom is frequently a kick in the head."

Illaoi.move26.text: "We are not one soul. We are many."

Illaoi.move27.text: "Many gods ask for worship. They are weak gods."

Illaoi.move28.text: "My god is not love - it is a kick in the pants."

Illaoi.move29.text: "Without change, something sleeps inside us, and seldom awakens."

Illaoi.move30.text: "Many die. Worthy souls find new forms."

Illaoi.move31.text: "Bearded Lady, Nagakabouros, names don't matter! Action does."

Illaoi.move32.text: "It is the storm that is life."

Illaoi.taunt01.text: "Live your life, chase what you desire, what else matters?"

Illaoi.taunt02.text: "A fool and his spirit are easily parted."

Illaoi.taunt03.text: "Watch your mouth, or I'll slap the soul out of you."

Illaoi.taunt04.text: "Fight me, if you have the spirit."

Illaoi.taunt05.text: "I want you to hit me as hard as you can."

Illaoi.taunt06.text: "Smile, child, or I'll shove your jaw into your brain."

Illaoi.tauntAscendant01.text: "You wanted to be a god! Instead, you are a useless antique!"

Illaoi.tauntAscendant02.text: "Foul creature, you would stop time when all things must move!"

Illaoi.tauntAscendant03.text: "You soul is a fetid, stagnant pool, untouched by the tide!"

Illaoi.tauntAscendant04.text: "You are not free from death! You are dead."

Illaoi.tauntAscendant05.text: "You powers are stolen from the flow. You have damned your homeland."

Illaoi.tauntDemacia01.text: "What is truly noble and good would never ask you to serve another!"

Illaoi.tauntDemacia02.text: "Duty, honor, nations? These are stagnant falsehoods!"

Illaoi.tauntDemacia03.text: "You are slaves enchained by lies when we were born to chase our desires!"

Illaoi.tauntDemacia04.text: "Laws, rules, these are falsehoods! Truth is chaos!"

Illaoi.tauntFiora01.text: "I do not challenge you, I bring you the test!"

Illaoi.tauntGaren01.text: "Honor? Duty? Ha! What your heart demands is all that matters."

Illaoi.tauntFreljord01.text: "Your people pretend to be strong. I think they are afraid."

Illaoi.tauntFreljord02.text: "Your people seek a worthy death. Mine, a worthy life."

Illaoi.tauntBraum01.text: "Northman. There are motions I would like to show you."

Illaoi.tauntBraum02.text: "I know you are strong. I wonder if you have stamina."

Illaoi.tauntGragas02.text: "You have followed our ways as if born to them."

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles01.text: "You are a cycle without purpose. I will end you!"
Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles01.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles02.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles03.text: "You are a cloud of broken souls, you are an abomination."
Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles03.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles04.text: "You will trouble this land no more."
Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles04.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles05.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles06.text: "I am your enemy because you offend my god - because you cannot change."
Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles06.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles07.text: "You will challenge me? Ha ha ha ha... even death fears my god."
Illaoi.tauntShadowIsles07.trigger: Taunting an Enemy Shadow Isles Champion

Illaoi.tauntYordle01.text: "Why would I need a spirit's help? I am guided by Nagakabouros."

Illaoi.tauntYordle02.text: "Little one, I don't need empathy. Seek those who do."

Illaoi.tauntYordle03.text: "Go back to where men are weak, and need your inspiration."

Illaoi.tauntAatrox01.text: "We know your true name. We do not fear you."

Illaoi.tauntAkali01.text: "Life is not balance. It is motion!"

Illaoi.tauntDiana01.text: "Your god was forgotten. Mine cannot be ignored."

Illaoi.tauntElise01.text: "False prophet! You don't even serve a true god!"

Illaoi.tauntDarius02.text: "You move well. Now, you must only find joy in the motion."

Illaoi.tauntGangplank01.text: "I broke men's hearts. I broke men's spines. You're the first who's going to get both."

Illaoi.tauntGangplank02.text: "You paid your tithe to the mother. Now show me what she taught you."

Illaoi.tauntGangplank03.text: "You have learned your lesson, now fight! Kill! Conquer!"

Illaoi.tauntGangplank05.text: "I do not want excuses. The failure was yours."

Illaoi.tauntGangplank06.text: "Did she not show you the way forward? Go!"

Illaoi.tauntJanna01.text: "The tempest is Nagakabouros. You serve, but are blind."

Illaoi.tauntJax01.text: "I do not challenge you, I bring you the test!"

Illaoi.tauntKarma01.text: "Trust the motion. All spirits are Nagakabouros'."

Illaoi.tauntKatarina01.text: "No love is impossible, my god demands you follow your desires."

Illaoi.tauntLeona01.text: "You worship the sun - it is my god that drives it through the sky."

Illaoi.tauntLeona02.text: "Your faith asks for obedience - it is weak."

Illaoi.tauntMissFortune02.text: "It is you who have shown Gangplank his path. For that, I thank you."

Illaoi.tauntMissFortune03.text: "Gangplank was drowning. Your actions reminded him to swim."

Illaoi.tauntRekSai01.text: "You are in motion - but only as a parasite on a host."

Illaoi.tauntRekSai02.text: "Ugly thing. You weren't designed by god, you were made by fools."

Illaoi.tauntRekSai04.text: "You are a foul creation - born from ignorance."

Illaoi.tauntRekSai05.text: "What kind of stupid god made you?"

Illaoi.tauntTahmKench01.text: "You move only from hunger that consumes itself."

Illaoi.tauntTahmKench02.text: "Creature, why would I listen to lies when I can see the truth?"

Illaoi.tauntTahmKench03.text: "Your fine words don't disguise your foul design."

Illaoi.tauntTwistedFate01.text: "Aw, child, you are cute, but I doubt you will be for long."

Illaoi.E10.text: "This is the motion. All is Nagakabouros."

Illaoi.E11.text: "I do not walk alone. I am with my god. It is here."

Illaoi.E12.text: "You cannot hide from god. You cannot hide from the test."

Illaoi.vessel01.text: "Live your journey - or die in mine."
Illaoi.vessel01.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel02.text: "Your spirit is held - take it if you can."
Illaoi.vessel02.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel03.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel04.text: "You speak of having a soul. It was never yours. None of them were."
Illaoi.vessel04.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel05.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel06.text: "Change, or you will be pulled down."
Illaoi.vessel06.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel07.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel08.text: "You are drowning - I want you to swim."
Illaoi.vessel08.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel09.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel10.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel11.text: "Each of your lives has served the vortex."
Illaoi.vessel11.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel12.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel13.text: "We learn from action. Move, or die."
Illaoi.vessel13.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel14.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel15.text: "This will be a good day - if you live."
Illaoi.vessel15.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel16.text: "Drive forward - it is destiny that calls you."
Illaoi.vessel16.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel17.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel18.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel19.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel20.text: "My god doesn't want you to kneel. It wants you to fight."
Illaoi.vessel20.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel21.text: "You have been given the tools to know your destiny."
Illaoi.vessel21.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel22.text: "The failure of your lives is written on your soul."
Illaoi.vessel22.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel23.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel24.text: "We are all free. Seeing the truth only reminds us."
Illaoi.vessel24.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel25.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel26.text: "All of us are lost, all of us are blind. You must swim towards your destiny."
Illaoi.vessel26.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel27.text: "Countless lifetimes lead our bodies foward, and drive our spirits towards their true destiny."
Illaoi.vessel27.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel28.text: "I don't want you to fail, I want you to learn."
Illaoi.vessel28.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel29.text: "Child, you must earn your soul. Prove yourself."
Illaoi.vessel29.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel30.text: "The battle is lost only when you surrender. Fight for your soul."
Illaoi.vessel30.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel31.text: "You are the tinest sliver of energy held briefly in shape. Where this energy flows is your destiny."
Illaoi.vessel31.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel32.text: "This moment is waiting to be seized."
Illaoi.vessel32.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel33.text: "Every day is waiting to be taken."
Illaoi.vessel33.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel34.text: "I don't want you to worship. I want you to learn."
Illaoi.vessel34.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel35.text: "I will break you if that's what it takes."
Illaoi.vessel35.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel36.text: "Give up, and your life is nothing."
Illaoi.vessel36.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.vessel37.text: "Each lifetime is a spirit. Each lifetime is a chance. Take it."
Illaoi.vessel37.trigger: While a Champion is an Active Vessel

Illaoi.item01.text: "It is not what we have, it is what we can throw away."

Illaoi.item02.text: "Things should be held only when we need them."

Illaoi.item03.text: "Only what moves, only what lives... has value."

Illaoi.item04.text: "When I am done with this... it will make a fine offering."

Illaoi.item05.text: "I like this. I should buy everyone one of these."

Illaoi.itemBootsBasic01.text: "I am going to walk all over them."

Illaoi.itemBootsAdvanced01.text: "My god is motion, but speed is useful."

Illaoi.itemRanduinsOmen01.text: "Who is Randuin? Was she a priestess?"

Illaoi.itemSteraksGage01.text: "Sterak? It is the fury of the mother I will bring."

Illaoi.itemTitanicHydra01.text: "The Kraken. The Serpent. The Hydra. A god's appearance is limited only by those observing it."

Illaoi.itemWarmogs01.text: "It is my god that protects me - but these metal clothes are nice."

Kalista.move16.text: "Nothing shall turn us from our path."

Kalista.joke01.text: "There will be no escape - I said no escape!"

Kalista.joke02.text: "We act as one - two - three - cease this!"

Kalista.taunt05.text: "Let's see how many spears you can endure!"

Kalista.taunt06.text: "Soft are the targets of our spears today!"

Kalista.tauntCassiopeia02.text: "You too shall have a blade in your back, snake."

Kalista.tauntGraves02.text: "Graves, you have only to speak our name."

Kalista.tauntKarthus01.text: "You toy with powers you do not comprehend, Deathsinger."

Kalista.tauntKarthus02.text: "Death is not solely your purview, Karthus."

Kalista.tauntKarthus03.text: "Only a fool would embrace death, Karthus."

Kalista.tauntLissandra01.text: "We see the course of your deception, Ice Witch."

Kalista.tauntVarus01.text: "There is no loss greater than betrayal, Varus."

Kalista.tauntVarus03.text: "You have pledged yourself to a false agent, Varus."

Kalista.itemInfinityEdge01.text: "Its edge is keen as the spear's tip."

Kalista.itemInfinityEdge02.text: "So shall others feel the bite of steel."

Kalista.itemLastWhisper02.text: "Nothing can protect them from our retribution."

Kalista.itemBloodthirster02.text: "As they weaken, so shall we grow stronger."

Kalista.itemBanshees03.text: "We will not be at the mercy of those who hide behind magic."

Kalista.itemBotRK01.text: "Once, he was a noble king, until grief overcame his reason."
Kalista.itemBotRK01.trigger: Upon purchasing Blade of the Ruined King

Kalista.itemBotRK02.text: "In the end, it was not his blade that stole our lives."
Kalista.itemBotRK02.trigger: Upon purchasing Blade of the Ruined King

Kalista.itemBotRK03.text: "As once it symbolized hope, so now shall it incite despair!"
Kalista.itemBotRK03.trigger: Upon purchasing Blade of the Ruined King
